    <title>P1019[NOIP2000提高组]单词接龙题解</title>
    <link href="http://ceres0,github.io/project/2022/01/19/P1019[NOIP2000%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%BB%84]%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E6%8E%A5%E9%BE%99%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3/"/>
    <id>http://ceres0,github.io/project/2022/01/19/P1019[NOIP2000%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%BB%84]%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E6%8E%A5%E9%BE%99%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3/</id>
    <published>2022-01-19T09:12:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-21T15:59:34.483Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="P1019-NOIP2000提高组-单词接龙"><a href="#P1019-NOIP2000提高组-单词接龙" class="headerlink" title="P1019[NOIP2000提高组]单词接龙"></a>P1019[NOIP2000提高组]单词接龙</h1><blockquote><h1 id="题目背景"><a href="#题目背景" class="headerlink" title="题目背景"></a>题目背景</h1><p>注意：本题为上古 NOIP 原题，不保证存在靠谱的做法能通过该数据范围下的所有数据。</p><h2 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h2><p>单词接龙是一个与我们经常玩的成语接龙相类似的游戏，现在我们已知一组单词，且给定一个开头的字母，要求出以这个字母开头的最长的“龙”（每个单词都最多在“龙”中出现两次），在两个单词相连时，其重合部分合为一部分，例如 beast 和 astonish，如果接成一条龙则变为 beastonish，另外相邻的两部分不能存在包含关系，例如 at 和 atide 间不能相连。</p><h2 id="输入格式"><a href="#输入格式" class="headerlink" title="输入格式"></a>输入格式</h2><p>输入的第一行为一个单独的整数n表示单词数，以下n行每行有一个单词，输入的最后一行为一个单个字符，表示“龙”开头的字母。你可以假定以此字母开头的“龙”一定存在。</p><h2 id="输出格式"><a href="#输出格式" class="headerlink" title="输出格式"></a>输出格式</h2><p>只需输出以此字母开头的最长的“龙”的长度。</p><h2 id="输入输出样例"><a href="#输入输出样例" class="headerlink" title="输入输出样例"></a>输入输出样例</h2><blockquote><h3 id="输入-1"><a href="#输入-1" class="headerlink" title="输入 #1"></a>输入 #1</h3><p>5<br>at<br>touch<br>cheat<br>choose<br>tact<br>a  </p><h3 id="输出-1"><a href="#输出-1" class="headerlink" title="输出 #1"></a>输出 #1</h3><p>23  </p></blockquote><h2 id="说明-提示"><a href="#说明-提示" class="headerlink" title="说明/提示"></a>说明/提示</h2><p>样例解释：连成的“龙”为 atoucheatactactouchoose。<br>n≤20</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="题目分析"><a href="#题目分析" class="headerlink" title="题目分析"></a>题目分析</h2><p>本题并不复杂，可以看出是一个字符串匹配+搜索遍历的算法。比较特殊的点有两个。一个是，本题的字符串匹配只存在于一个字符串的前缀和另一个字符串的后缀之间的匹配，相对易于解决一些；另一个是，搜索时每个点可经历两次而非一次。为了方便算法的描述，将本题的算法分为两个部分，建图部分和搜索部分。</p><h3 id="建图部分"><a href="#建图部分" class="headerlink" title="建图部分"></a>建图部分</h3><p>分析题面可以知道，在这个图中，结点为一个一个单词，而如果两个单词（字符串）前后缀中存在重叠部分，则两者间存在一条边，且由于本题所求单词数最多，所以只需考虑最短的重叠部分即可，而边权即为加上这个单词后这条“龙”的增加长度。考虑到这里需要解决的一个问题是，如何获取两个字符串的前后缀重叠部分。<br>首先一个简单的方法就是将一个字符串的每一个后缀与另一个的字符串进行比较，得到一个重复的字符串，显然这样子写会非常麻烦，且时间复杂度较高，这里可以考虑使用一个类似动归的方法，从后一个字符串的前缀中每次去一个字符在前一个字符串中查找相同的字符，如果这个字符前的动归数组值与轮次-1相同，则使此位置的动归数组与轮次相同。二维数组的递推公式如下：<br>$f(x,i)=\begin{cases}<br>    i, &amp;字符相同时且f(x-1,i-1)==i-1\<br>    0, &amp;others<br>\end{cases}$<br>此时，由于得到最短重叠部分，所以只需要$f(字符串最后一位)$不为0时，动归结束，重叠部分的最短部分长度为$f(字符串最后一位)$的值。边权为后一个字符串长度减去重叠部分长度。为节省空间，使用一位数组的递推公式如下：<br>$f(x)=\begin{cases}<br>    i, &amp;字符相同时且f(x)==i-1\<br>    0, &amp;others<br>\end{cases}$<br>此时需要注意的是，循环要从后往前进行以防轮次混乱。  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int mixl(string a,string b)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int f[a.length()];</span><br><span class="line">int len=a.length()-1;</span><br><span class="line">memset(f,0,sizeof(f));</span><br><span class="line">for(int i=0;i&lt;b.length();i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">for(int j=len;j&gt;=i;j--)</span><br><span class="line">if(a[j]==b[i] &amp;&amp; (!i || f[j-1]==i))</span><br><span class="line">f[j]=i+1;</span><br><span class="line">if(f[len])</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">return f[len];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>另一种方向就是一编码复杂度换时间，将用一个新的数组去存后缀中含有前缀中某一字符的位置，可以用vector来动态存储。首先将前一个字符的每一位加入vector中，然后取后一个字符串中前缀的第一个字符，并取vector中的位置的下一位字符进行比较，如果相同就放入vector中，然后取后一个字符串前缀的第二个字符，然后在与vector中的对比，一次类推，直到位置中出现了前一个字符串的最后一个位置，此时轮次即为重叠的部分。（这个挖个坑，之后想练手可能实现一下。<br>然后就是建图。本算法采用邻接矩阵存取，占用空间较小。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">struct Edge&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Edge *next;</span><br><span class="line">int v;//该边指向点的编号</span><br><span class="line">int val;//边权</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;//邻接表存边</span><br><span class="line">struct Node&#123;</span><br><span class="line">string s;</span><br><span class="line">Edge *fe;//首边</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后用一个类来存储该图。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">class Graph&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Node *v;//点集</span><br><span class="line">int nv;//点的总数</span><br><span class="line">int *times;//访问次数</span><br><span class="line">public:</span><br><span class="line">Graph()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">nv=0;</span><br><span class="line">v=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">times=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Graph(int);</span><br><span class="line">void addEdge(int,int,int);//加边</span><br><span class="line">void Judge(char);//解决问题</span><br><span class="line">int Dfs(int);//遍历函数</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="搜索部分"><a href="#搜索部分" class="headerlink" title="搜索部分"></a>搜索部分</h3><p>由于是遍历出所有的可能性，求其中的最大值，所以DFS和BFS的效率几乎没有区别，所以本题采用较为易写的DFS进行搜索。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void Graph::Judge(char c)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int ans=0,t;</span><br><span class="line">for(int i=0;i&lt;nv;i++)</span><br><span class="line">if(v[i].s[0]==c)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">t=v[i].s.length()+Dfs(i);</span><br><span class="line">ans=t&gt;ans?t:ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;ans&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">int Graph::Dfs(int u)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int ans=0,t;</span><br><span class="line">times[u]++;</span><br><span class="line">for(Edge *p=v[u].fe;p!=NULL;p=p-&gt;next)</span><br><span class="line">if(times[p-&gt;v]&lt;2)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">t=p-&gt;val+Dfs(p-&gt;v);</span><br><span class="line">ans=ans&gt;t?ans:t;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">times[u]--;</span><br><span class="line">return ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后得出结果。</p><h2 id="完整代码"><a href="#完整代码" class="headerlink" title="完整代码"></a>完整代码</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">struct Edge&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Edge *next;</span><br><span class="line">int v;//该边指向点的编号</span><br><span class="line">int val;//边权</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;//邻接表存边</span><br><span class="line">struct Node&#123;</span><br><span class="line">string s;</span><br><span class="line">Edge *fe;//首边</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">class Graph&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Node *v;//点集</span><br><span class="line">int nv;//点的总数</span><br><span class="line">int *times;//访问次数</span><br><span class="line">public:</span><br><span class="line">Graph()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">nv=0;</span><br><span class="line">v=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">times=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Graph(int);</span><br><span class="line">void addEdge(int,int,int);//加边</span><br><span class="line">void Judge(char);//解决问题</span><br><span class="line">int Dfs(int);//遍历函数</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int mixl(string a,string b);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int n=0;</span><br><span class="line">char c;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;n;</span><br><span class="line">Graph g(n);</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;c;</span><br><span class="line">g.Judge(c);</span><br><span class="line">// string a,b;</span><br><span class="line">// cin&gt;&gt;a&gt;&gt;b;</span><br><span class="line">// cout&lt;&lt;mixl(a,b);</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Graph::Graph(int n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">nv=n;</span><br><span class="line">v=new Node[n];//动态数组</span><br><span class="line">times=new int[n];</span><br><span class="line">for(int i=0;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;v[i].s;</span><br><span class="line">v[i].fe=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">times[i]=0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">for(int j=0;j&lt;=i;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int l=mixl(v[i].s,v[j].s),len=v[j].s.length();</span><br><span class="line">if(l &amp;&amp; l&lt;len)</span><br><span class="line">addEdge(i,j,len-l);</span><br><span class="line">if(j&lt;i)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">l=mixl(v[j].s,v[i].s);len=v[i].s.length();</span><br><span class="line">if(l &amp;&amp; l&lt;len)</span><br><span class="line">addEdge(j,i,len-l);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">void Graph::addEdge(int a,int b,int w)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Edge *p=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">// cout&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;&#x27; &#x27;&lt;&lt;b&lt;&lt;&#x27; &#x27;&lt;&lt;w&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">if(v[a].fe!=NULL)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">p=v[a].fe;</span><br><span class="line">while(p-&gt;next!=NULL)</span><br><span class="line">p=p-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">p-&gt;next=new Edge;</span><br><span class="line">p=p-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">p-&gt;v=b;</span><br><span class="line">p-&gt;val=w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">p=new Edge;</span><br><span class="line">v[a].fe=p;</span><br><span class="line">p-&gt;v=b;</span><br><span class="line">p-&gt;val=w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">void Graph::Judge(char c)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int ans=0,t;</span><br><span class="line">for(int i=0;i&lt;nv;i++)</span><br><span class="line">if(v[i].s[0]==c)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">t=v[i].s.length()+Dfs(i);</span><br><span class="line">ans=t&gt;ans?t:ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;ans&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">int Graph::Dfs(int u)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int ans=0,t;</span><br><span class="line">times[u]++;</span><br><span class="line">for(Edge *p=v[u].fe;p!=NULL;p=p-&gt;next)</span><br><span class="line">if(times[p-&gt;v]&lt;2)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">t=p-&gt;val+Dfs(p-&gt;v);</span><br><span class="line">ans=ans&gt;t?ans:t;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">times[u]--;</span><br><span class="line">return ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int mixl(string a,string b)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int f[a.length()];</span><br><span class="line">int len=a.length()-1;</span><br><span class="line">memset(f,0,sizeof(f));</span><br><span class="line">for(int i=0;i&lt;b.length();i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">for(int j=len;j&gt;=i;j--)</span><br><span class="line">if(a[j]==b[i] &amp;&amp; (!i || f[j-1]==i))</span><br><span class="line">f[j]=i+1;</span><br><span class="line">// for(int j=0;j&lt;=len;j++)</span><br><span class="line">// cout&lt;&lt;f[j]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">// cout&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">if(f[len])</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">return f[len];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
